{"tid":2488739,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"日本Kagome人權考量停用新疆番茄　葛珮帆稱估到：會支持新疆番茄","createTime":"2021-04-14T12:16:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-14T13:25:59.000Z","uid":230530,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7a5cb715d85a0af9d7c5d33633ad7d036f174a1f","tid":2488739,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T12:16:16.000Z","msg":"「新疆棉風波」持續發酵，《日本經濟新聞》今（14日）報道，被稱為日本「番茄醬之王」的「可果美」（Kagome）會在本年內停用新疆的番茄，除了因為成本和品質外，當地人權問題亦是考量之一，Kagome強調以往採購的新疆番茄並非侵犯人權所得，是首間日本大型企業因新疆問題停用當地產品。<br />\n記者到日資超級市場「驚安」貨架上，仍發現大量KAGOME茄汁出售，價值為20元至30元，現場所見未有市民搶購情況。而建制派議員葛珮帆則表示日本作為美國盟友，出手打擊中國是意料中事，又稱自己每天都會吃番茄，但沒有留意產地，以後若見到有新疆番茄將會購入支持。"},{"pid":"8bf0de645f233980b1281c201bdc846602c3abf9","tid":2488739,"uid":387649,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T12:17:47.000Z","msg":"之前開會唔係仲諗緊買邊隻台灣芒?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04125a792e4f39bb1f8060b747e7e1015e11f4c3","tid":2488739,"uid":11291,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T12:22:22.000Z","msg":"葛佩帆買芒果<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmapGp41eyXzMgVQ9PC5HEruXWPZTms5ia5dC7pt8LEQAN?filename=cRxrPvk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcRxrPvk.jpg&h=fff000d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSjqJysHJP7dbWEaDWXAKm2hPqrwDaomuPA6c3nUNuk1U?filename=2Xz543G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2Xz543G.jpg&h=8e334bb7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"84eacfa4f47d78b7f9ee0b5dcc26a5e73133277e","tid":2488739,"uid":290118,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T12:29:12.000Z","msg":"佢真係好撚煩"},{"pid":"599a6b75db43ab8ca1d7ab9502cd72b2b1cd1446","tid":2488739,"uid":123738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T13:11:55.000Z","msg":"支那狗又多好多蕃茄食啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/